Installation root directory:
============================

	/usr/local

Application directory structure:
================================

	/usr/local/[application]/
		bin
		conf
		log

Pid files:
==========

	/usr/local/[application]/log/[application].pid

Log files:
==========

	1) File names
		[application].log
		[application].err

	2) Location

		/var/log/
		/usr/local/[application]/log/ (symbolic links)
